rows.label: qst500206_msg0101
rows.name:
Cave of Acedia so comfy, Foorara stayed
there for very long time...

rows.label: qst500206_msg0102
rows.name:
But then ground start shaking
very lots, and suddenly World Tree
in front of eyes!

rows.label: qst500206_msg0103
rows.name: Foorara never more shock in all of life!

rows.label: qst500206_msg0104
rows.name:
After that Foorara follow other people
to boat and escape Acedia safe.

rows.label: qst500206_msg0105
rows.name: Foorara very lucky to be living!

rows.label: qst500206_msg0106
rows.name:
Anyway, Voltis Trade Guild Walky-
Walky Guide Book say, no matter how
hard things get, always keep going.

rows.label: qst500206_msg0107
rows.name:
People here was very helpful, but
Foorara must go on with Walky-Walky!

rows.label: qst500206_msg0108
rows.name:
Quite tired of hot place now,
so probably go to Luxuria next!
